bill.summary: 5/13/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1994, the duty on n,n-dimethyl-n'(3-((methylamino)-carbonyl)oxy)-phenyl)-methanimidamide monohydrochloride.
